event.title: GBE10 Whole Shebang 2016
event.description: A full weekend of burlesque -- shows, classes, exhibits, shopping, and more!
event.e_description: The Great Burlesque Exposition of 2016 takes place Feb. 5-7, 2016 in Cambridge, MA. Our tenth year features exciting special guests, a conference that will change your professional life, and many new events and activities just for this year!
